trans-unit.source: QLCDNumber emits the overflow() signal when it is asked to display something beyond its range. The range is set by setDigitCount(), but setSmallDecimalPoint() also influences it. If the display is set to hexadecimal, octal or binary, the integer equivalent of the value is displayed.
trans-unit.target: 当要求其显示超出其范围的内容时，QLCDNumber发出overflow（）信号。范围是由setDigitCount（）设置的，但是setSmallDecimalPoint（）也会影响它。如果显示设置为十六进制，八进制或二进制，则显示该值的整数等效值。

trans-unit.source: QLabel is used for displaying text or an image. No user interaction functionality is provided. The visual appearance of the label can be configured in various ways, and it can be used for specifying a focus mnemonic key for another widget.
trans-unit.target: QLabel用于显示文本或图像。不提供用户交互功能。标签的视觉外观可以以各种方式配置,它可用于为另一个小组件指定焦点记号键。

trans-unit.source: QLayerFilter can be configured to select or discard entities with a specific QLayer depending on the filterMode property. By default, entities referencing one of the QLayer objects that are also being referenced by the QLayerFilter are selected (AcceptAnyMatchingLayers).
trans-unit.target: 可以将QLayerFilter配置为选择或丢弃具有特定QLayer的实体，具体取决于filterMode属性。默认情况下，引用的一个实体QLayer其也正在被引用的对象QLayerFilter被选择（AcceptAnyMatchingLayers）。

trans-unit.source: QLerpClipBlend can be useful to create advanced animation effects based on individual animation clips. For instance, given a player character, lerp blending could be used to combine a walking animation clip with an injured animation clip based on a blend factor that increases the more the player gets injured. This would then allow with blend factor == 0 to have a non injured walking player, with blend factor == 1 a fully injured player, with blend factor == 0.5 a partially walking and injured player.
trans-unit.target: QLerpClipBlend可以用来创建基于单个动画片段的高级动画效果。例如,给定一个玩家角色,lerp blending可以用来结合一个行走的动画片段和一个受伤的动画片段,基于一个混合因子,玩家受伤越多,混合因子就越大。这将允许在混合因子==0的情况下有一个非受伤的行走玩家,混合因子==1的情况下有一个完全受伤的玩家,混合因子==0.5的情况下有一个部分行走和受伤的玩家。

trans-unit.source: QLevelOfDetail can be used to control the representation of an entity based on distance from the observer or size on the screen.
trans-unit.target: QLevelOfDetail可以用来控制实体的表示,基于与观察者的距离或屏幕上的大小。

trans-unit.source: QLinkedList<T> is one of Qt's generic container classes. It stores a list of values and provides iterator-based access as well as constant time insertions and removals.
trans-unit.target: QLinkedList <T>是Qt的通用容器类之一。它存储值列表，并提供基于迭代器的访问以及固定时间的插入和删除。

trans-unit.source: QLinkedList's value type must be an assignable data type. This covers most data types that are commonly used, but the compiler won't let you, for example, store a QWidget as a value; instead, store a QWidget *. A few functions have additional requirements; for example, contains() and removeAll() expect the value type to support operator==(). These requirements are documented on a per-function basis.

trans-unit.source: QList provides these basic functions to add, move, and remove items: insert(), replace(), remove(), prepend(), append(). With the exception of append(), prepend() and replace(), these functions can be slow (linear time) for large lists, because they require moving many items in the list by one position in memory. If you want a container class that provides fast insertion/removal in the middle, use std::list instead.
trans-unit.target: QList提供了以下基本功能来添加，移动和删除项目：insert（），replace（），remove（），prepend（），append（）。除了append（），prepend（）和replace（）以外，对于大型列表，这些函数可能会很慢（线性时间），因为它们需要将列表中的许多项移动到内存中的一个位置。如果要在中间提供快速插入/移除的容器类，请改用std :: list。

trans-unit.source: QList provides these basic functions to add, move, and remove items: insert(), replace(), removeAt(), move(), and swap(). In addition, it provides the following convenience functions: append(), operator<<(), operator+=(), prepend(), removeFirst(), and removeLast().
trans-unit.target: QList提供了以下基本功能来添加，移动和删除项目：insert（），replace（），removeAt（），move（）和swap（）。此外，它还提供以下便利功能：append（），operator <<（），operator + =（），prepend（），removeFirst（）和removeLast（）。
